name: Enhanced KeePass 2.14.1
short_description: This is an enhanced version of KeePass 2.14.1 with an additional feature of window title conflict resolution. KeePass has been enhanced so that, in case there is more than one entry in a KeePass DB with same or similar(wildcard characters involved here), then KeePass will first check the URL's of the conflicting entries and decide accordingly thereby reducing the pop-up window presented every time there is such a conflict. In case there is no URL mentioned in any one of the entries, then only KeePass will take the window title configured for that entry into consideration.
summary: This is an enhancemened version of KeePass 2.14.1
